<div class="content line">
<h2><a id="signup"></a>Become a member of the Marrakesh Treaty</h2>
<div class="main">
<p class="lead">All <a href="/members/en/">WIPO member states</a> are eligible to become party to the Marrakesh Treaty. To become a member, a state must deposit an "instrument" declaring its intention with the <a href="/about-wipo/en/dg_gurry/">Director General of WIPO</a>. This instrument must be signed by the Head of State, the Head of Government or the Minister of Foreign Affairs.</p>
<h3>Legislative assistance</h3>
<p>As part of its mission, WIPO is always ready to respond to member state requests for review of national legislation in light of treaty provisions.</p>
<p><a href="https://www3.wipo.int/contact/en/area.jsp?area=copyright">Contact us</a> to find out more.</p>
</div>
